snippet.title: Boingkid™ and Chambers of Destiny (Kickstarter Trailer)
snippet.description:
Back Us on Kickstarter:
https://goo.gl/25xK21

 Boingkid™ is a newcomer into the magical & mysterious Realm of Toys. He's an innocent little toy with no instruction manual who has no idea of the hidden purpose in his creation and design.
Boing in to reveal the mystery behind Boingkid's identity in this all new 2D action puzzle platformer adventure.
You can buy the Early access version: https://niv-studio.itch.io/boingkid-ea
